      <title>枫叶一片，寄上想念</title>
      <link href="/2018/12/30/%E6%9E%AB%E5%8F%B6%E4%B8%80%E7%89%87%E5%AF%84%E4%B8%8A%E6%83%B3%E5%BF%B5/"/>
      <url>/2018/12/30/%E6%9E%AB%E5%8F%B6%E4%B8%80%E7%89%87%E5%AF%84%E4%B8%8A%E6%83%B3%E5%BF%B5/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p></p><h4 style="text-align:center">枫叶一片，寄上想念 </h4><p></p><div align="center"><br><h4 style="text-align:right"> —— 老大   </h4><br><div align="center"><br><img src="https://www.z4a.net/images/2018/12/30/140a28a8ae3e9182f.jpg"><br></div><br>&nbsp;<br><br>&emsp;&emsp;今天是在一起的155天，美好的那个夏天<br>&nbsp;<br>&emsp;&emsp;至今还很庆幸<br>&nbsp;<br>&emsp;&emsp;我们的那些日子<br>&nbsp;<br>&emsp;&emsp;虽然已经逝去但是依然存在<br>&nbsp;<br>&emsp;&emsp;总是在清晨入眠，思考着这一夜<br>&nbsp;<br>&emsp;&emsp;到底带来了什么<br>&nbsp;<br>&emsp;&emsp;有时夜很短<br>&nbsp;<br>&emsp;&emsp;刚进入梦乡不久天已亮<br>&nbsp;<br>&emsp;&emsp;有时夜很长<br>&nbsp;<br>&emsp;&emsp;长到有数不完的绵羊后面数不完的狼<br>&nbsp;<br>&emsp;&emsp;然后幸福却悄悄降临<br>&nbsp;<br>&emsp;&emsp;惊喜、不安、茫然、清醒、坚定<br>&nbsp;<br>&emsp;&emsp;或许早已是上天的安排<br>&nbsp;<br>&emsp;&emsp;我开始疯狂的填满你的内心<br>&nbsp;<br>&emsp;&emsp;充斥着爱与渴望<br>&nbsp;<br>&emsp;&emsp;无数隔空相对的夜晚，不能安然入睡<br>&nbsp;<br>&emsp;&emsp;听不够的悄悄话，看不厌的眼前人<br>&nbsp;<br>&emsp;&emsp;我要和你一起<br>&nbsp;<br>&emsp;&emsp;走在青山绿水之间<br>&nbsp;<br>&emsp;&emsp;牵着你的手<br>&nbsp;<br>&emsp;&emsp;走过这座桥，翻过那座山<br>&nbsp;<br>&emsp;&emsp;山脚下鲜花烂漫，山顶山云卷云舒<br>&nbsp;<br>&emsp;&emsp;山的那边是清晨，山的这边是日暮<br>&nbsp;<br>&emsp;&emsp;于是我拾起山间那一片片枫叶<br>&nbsp;<br>&emsp;&emsp;遥寄思念与爱恋<br><br><br><div align="center"><br><img src="https://www.z4a.net/images/2018/12/30/2f612920b1bd216bd.jpg"><br></div></div>]]></content>
      
      
